---
title: Spiced Tomato Veggie Mince Ragu with Peas, Cheese and Buttery Mash
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Spiced Tomato Pork Mince Ragu in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R14_W25_UK_QF11592-30_Main_Plant_Based_Burger_edit_high-aae02337.jpg
